---

### 5. CARGO ALIASES

**File**: `/Users/ericson/Workspace/Rust/ars-ui/.cargo/config.toml` (lines 1-10):

```toml
[alias]
xtask        = "run --package xtask --"          # Direct xtask invocation
xci          = "xtask ci"                         # Full CI pipeline
xci-fast     = "xtask ci --profile fast"          # Fast pre-push gate (~5 min)
xclippy      = "xtask clippy"                     # Interactive clippy (no -D warnings)
xfmt         = "run --quiet --package xtask -- fmt"  # Workspace format
xmcp         = "xtask mcp"                        # MCP server
